                           certainty="circa"
                           era="ce"
                           calendar="gregorian">8 September [1751]</date>.
							First published, as <title render="doublequote" linktype="simple">Hymn to
							Adversity</title>, in <extref href="http://www.thomasgray.org/resources/glnames.shtml#Dodsley, Robert, 1703-1764"
                             show="replace"
