                        <persname normal="Dodsley, Robert, 1703-1764">Dodsley</persname>'s</extref>
                     <title render="italic" linktype="simple">Designs</title> (<date normal="1753" type="publication" era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1753</date>), <extref href="http://www.thomasgray.org/cgi-bin/view.cgi?collection=primary&amp;edition=1753&amp;text=otad"
                             show="replace"
                             linktype="simple">[24]</extref>.
						</p>
